--Jave JDK Installation

Step 1 : Jave installation

sudo apt update
sudo apt install openjdk-11-jdk
Java --version

Step 2: Tomcat tar download   (cd /opt)

sudo wget https://mirrors.estointernet.in/apache/tomcat/tomcat-9/v9.0.45/bin/apache-tomcat-9.0.45.tar.gz

Step 3: Unzip tar file

tar -zvxf <filename>

Step 4: Start tomcat

/bin/ startup.sh